problem_text_en: As shown in the figure, it is known that in Rt△ABC, ∠C = N_0, AB = N_1, AC = N_2, then the value of tanB is ()
raw_answer:
解:在Rt△ABC中,由勾股定理,得
BC=√{AB^{2}-AC^{2}}=√{10^{2}-8^{2}}=6,
由正切函数的意义,得
tanB=\frac{AC}{BC}=\frac{8}{6}=\frac{4}{3},
故选:D．
raw_comment: 本题考查了锐角三角函数的定义,利用正切函数等于对边比邻边是解题关键．
